<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
  <title>Blossom Grace | Light Pink Scripture Sanctuary</title>
  <!-- Google Fonts: Playfair Display + Inter -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;1,400;1,500&family=Inter:opsz,wght@14..32,300;14..32,400;14..32,500;14..32,600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      background: #fff9fb;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      color: #5e3a4e;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ----- Navigation Bar (matching pink aesthetic) ----- */
    .navbar {
      background: rgba(255, 245, 248, 0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #ffe2ea;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
    }

    .logo a {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e899b5, #f5aec8);
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2.2rem;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #c86f8f;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      font-size: 1rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: #e07ea2;
      background: #ffeef3;
      padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 40px;
    }

    /* ---------- COVER SECTION (soft pink dream) ---------- */
    .cover {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbc4d5, #f8a5c2);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .cover-bg-img {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      opacity: 0.2;
      z-index: 1;
      filter: brightness(0.95) contrast(1.05) blur(1.5px);
      transition: transform 12s ease;
    }

    .cover:hover .cover-bg-img {
      transform: scale(1.02);
    }

    .cover-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      max-width: 780px;
      background: rgba(255, 235, 240, 0.55);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 3rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 200, 210, 0.6);
      box-shadow: 0 35px 50px -20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 220, 230, 0.5);
      animation: pinkGlow 4s infinite alternate;
    }

    @keyframes pinkGlow {
      0% { box-shadow: 0 35px 50px -20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); border-color: rgba(255, 190, 200, 0.5); }
      100% { box-shadow: 0 45px 60px -15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25); border-color: rgba(255, 210, 220, 0.9); }
    }

    .cover-content h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7cad0, #f2a0b5);
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .cover-content p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #fce4ea;
      margin: 1rem 0;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .btn-enter {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(95deg, #f5a0b9, #f07d9e);
      padding: 0.9rem 2.4rem;
      border-radius: 60px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-top: 1.8rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .btn-enter:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(95deg, #ffb0c6, #ff8aad);
      transform: scale(1.02);
    }

    /* ---------- MAIN CONTENT (light pink aesthetic) ---------- */
    .main-content {
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem 2rem 5rem;
      display: none;
    }

    .aesthetic-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
      position: relative;
      color: #d47a9a;
    }
    .aesthetic-title:after {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 85px;
      height: 3px;
      background: #f3b0c2;
      margin: 12px auto 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .poster-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 2rem;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
    }

    .scripture-card {
      background: rgba(255, 252, 253, 0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
      border-radius: 2.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 35px -18px rgba(180, 100, 120, 0.15);
      padding: 2rem 1.8rem;
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 280px;
      transition: all 0.35s ease;
      border: 1px solid #ffe2ea;
    }

    .scripture-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 30px 42px -15px rgba(200, 100, 130, 0.25);
      border-color: #ffcfdd;
      background: #ffffff;
    }

    .verse-icon {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      color: #f28aa8;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .verse-ref-styled {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2.5px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #d16a90;
      background: #ffeef3;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.2rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 50px;
    }

    .verse-large {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin: 1rem 0 0.8rem;
      color: #b5577a;
    }

    .verse-text-body {
      color: #a16b82;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-top: 0.8rem;
    }

    /* PINK ALERT POSTER */
    .alert-masterpiece {
      background: linear-gradient(125deg, #f5cddb, #fdb7cb);
      border-radius: 3rem;
      padding: 2.2rem;
      margin: 3rem 0;
      box-shadow: 0 28px 40px -18px #e79aba;
      border: 1px solid #ffc0d0;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .alert-masterpiece:before {
      content: "🦁";
      font-size: 140px;
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -20px;
      right: -20px;
      opacity: 0.1;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .alert-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #b34e73;
    }

    .roar-text {
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #a33f63;
      margin: 0.7rem 0;
    }

    .resist-block {
      background: rgba(255, 220, 230, 0.7);
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.8rem;
      border-radius: 60px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 1rem 0;
      backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
      color: #a14064;
    }

    .pink-quote {
      background: #fff5f8;
      border-radius: 2rem;
      padding: 1.8rem;
      border-left: 10px solid #f59fba;
      margin: 1.8rem 0;
    }

    .music-suggestion {
      background: #ffeef3;
      border-radius: 3rem;
      padding: 1.2rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      border: 1px solid #ffdee8;
    }

    .music-badge i {
      margin-right: 8px;
      color: #f085a6;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #ffe0ea;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #cf8aaa;
    }

    .pink-tag {
      background: #ffeef3;
      padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 40px;
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #ce7c9c;
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .cover-content h1 { font-size: 2.3rem; }
      .verse-large { font-size: 1.45rem; }
      .aesthetic-title { font-size: 2rem; }
      .roar-text { font-size: 1.3rem; }
      .navbar {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .nav-links {
        gap: 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Navigation Bar (updated with link to program.html) -->
<div class="navbar">
  <div class="logo"><a href="index.html">🌸 Blossom Grace</a></div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="index.html"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Home</a></li>
    <li><a href="program.html"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> Programs</a></li>
    <li><a href="#verses"><i class="fas fa-bible"></i> Verses</a></li>
    <li><a href="#music"><i class="fas fa-music"></i> Worship</a></li>
  </ul>
</div>

<!-- COVER: soft pink -->
<div id="coverSection" class="cover">
  <img class="cover-bg-img" id="coverImg" alt="Pink sanctuary" src="picture.png">
  <div class="cover-content">
    <i class="fas fa-feather-alt" style="font-size: 3rem; color: #ffccda; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"></i>
    <h1>All Your Needs<br>According to His Riches</h1>
    <p>Philippians 4:19 · The Merciful · Standing Firm in Faith</p>
    <button class="btn-enter" id="enterBtn"><i class="fas fa-heart"></i> Enter the Pink Peace <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></button>
    <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 1.3rem; opacity: 0.9;">“Blessed are the merciful, for they will be shown mercy.” — Matthew 5:7</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MAIN PINK CONTENT -->
<div id="mainContent" class="main-content">
  <div class="aesthetic-title" id="verses">
    <i class="fas fa-scroll" style="font-size: 2rem; opacity: 0.8; color: #f096b4;"></i><br>
    ✿ verses of mercy & watchfulness ✿
  </div>

  <div class="poster-grid">
    <div class="scripture-card">
      <div class="verse-icon"><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i></div>
      <div class="verse-ref-styled">Providence · Promise</div>
      <div class="verse-large">“And my God will meet <strong>all your needs</strong> according to the riches of his glory in Christ Jesus.”</div>
      <div class="verse-ref-styled" style="background: #ffeef3;">PHILIPPIANS 4:19</div>
      <div class="verse-text-body">No lack can linger — His riches in glory overflow. Rest in divine abundance.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="scripture-card">
      <div class="verse-icon"><i class="fas fa-dove"></i></div>
      <div class="verse-ref-styled">Beatitude · Mercy</div>
      <div class="verse-large">“Blessed are the merciful, for they will be shown mercy.”</div>
      <div class="verse-ref-styled" style="background: #ffeef3;">MATTHEW 5:7</div>
      <div class="verse-text-body">Kindness is a heavenly mirror — when we forgive, mercy flows back like soft pink petals.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 1 PETER 5:8-9 ALERT POSTER pink edition -->
  <div class="alert-masterpiece">
    <div class="alert-title"><i class="fas fa-shield-virus"></i> · WATCH & PRAY ·</div>
    <div class="roar-text">BE ALERT! &nbsp;|&nbsp; OF SOBER MIND</div>
    <div style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 500; color: #b5466b; margin: 0.5rem 0;">Your enemy the devil prowls around like a roaring lion <br> looking for someone to devour.</div>
    <div class="resist-block"><i class="fas fa-crosshairs"></i> RESIST HIM — STANDING FIRM IN THE FAITH</div>
    <div style="margin-top: 1rem; color: #b75278; font-style: italic;">“Because you know that the family of believers throughout the world is undergoing the same kind of sufferings.”</div>
    <div class="verse-ref-styled" style="background: #ffd9e4; color:#b34e73; margin-top: 0.8rem;">1 PETER 5:8-9</div>
  </div>

  <div class="poster-grid">
    <div class="scripture-card">
      <i class="fas fa-feather-alt" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #f09ebc;"></i>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display'; margin: 0.5rem 0;">The Merciful Receive Mercy</h3>
      <p>Matthew 5:7 reveals the rhythm of heaven. When you release bitterness, you invite divine tenderness into your life.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="scripture-card">
      <i class="fas fa-crown" style="font-size: 2rem; color:#f09ebc;"></i>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display'; margin: 0.5rem 0;">Riches in Glory</h3>
      <p>Philippians 4:19 declares every need—emotional, spiritual, relational—is supplied from God's glorious treasure chest.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="scripture-card">
      <i class="fas fa-lion" style="font-size: 2rem; color:#f09ebc;"></i>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display'; margin: 0.5rem 0;">Sober-Minded Victory</h3>
      <p>1 Peter 5:8-9 calls us to alertness. The enemy prowls, but the global family stands united in faith.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="pink-quote">
    <i class="fas fa-candle-light" style="font-size: 2rem; float: left; margin-right: 1rem; color: #f598b6;"></i>
    <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display'; font-weight: 600;">✧ Personal Devotion & Growth ✧</h3>
    <p><strong>📖 Bible Verse for Today:</strong> “Be alert and of sober mind. Your enemy the devil prowls around like a roaring lion looking for someone to devour.” (1 Peter 5:8)</p>
    <p><strong>⚡ Moral of the Verse:</strong> Always be watchful — the enemy seeks moments of spiritual drowsiness. Through prayer and God's Word, we remain steadfast. “Resist him, standing firm in the faith.”</p>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.8rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
      <span class="pink-tag"><i class="fas fa-share-alt"></i> Sharing Your Faith</span>
      <span class="pink-tag"><i class="fas fa-hand-peace"></i> Choosing Forgiveness</span>
      <span class="pink-tag"><i class="fas fa-heart"></i> 1 Corinthians 13 — Love's Greatness</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="music-suggestion" id="music">
    <div class="music-badge"><i class="fas fa-headphones-alt fa-fw"></i> <strong>GOSPEL PLAYLIST (Pink edition)</strong> — Way Maker, What A Beautiful Name, Goodness of God, Reckless Love</div>
    <div><i class="fas fa-church"></i> Let worship keep your spirit alert</div>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #fff2f6; border-radius: 2rem; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; text-align: center; border:1px solid #ffdee8;">
    <i class="fas fa-heart" style="color: #f47ca0;"></i> <strong>1 Corinthians 13 deep dive:</strong> Love is patient, kind, and never fails. Jesus modeled perfect love — may this be your daily anthem.
  </div>

  <footer>
    <i class="fas fa-feather"></i> “Resist him, standing firm in the faith, because you know that the family of believers throughout the world is undergoing the same sufferings.” — 1 Peter 5:9 <br>
    <span style="font-size: 1rem;">✨ THANK YOU — May His mercy and provision guard your heart like a garden of roses ✨</span>
    <div class="verse-ref-styled" style="background: none; margin-top: 0.8rem; color: #e08aaa;">BIBLE POSTER — All your needs · Mercy · Lion of Judah</div>
  </footer>
</div>

<script>
  const coverImage = document.getElementById('coverImg');
  if (coverImage) {
    coverImage.src = "picture.png";
    coverImage.onerror = function() {
      this.src = "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1510798831971-661eb04b3739?w=1600&auto=format";
      this.style.opacity = "0.25";
    };
  }

  const enterBtn = document.getElementById('enterBtn');
  const coverSec = document.getElementById('coverSection');
  const mainSec = document.getElementById('mainContent');

  if (enterBtn && coverSec && mainSec) {
    enterBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      coverSec.style.transition = "opacity 0.8s ease, visibility 0s linear 0.8s";
      coverSec.style.opacity = "0";
      setTimeout(() => {
        coverSec.style.display = "none";
        mainSec.style.display = "block";
        window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: "smooth" });
        document.body.style.background = "#fff9fb";
        mainSec.style.animation = "pinkFade 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.2,0.9,0.4,1.1)";
      }, 750);
    });
  }

  const dynamicStyle = document.createElement('style');
  dynamicStyle.textContent = `
    @keyframes pinkFade {
      0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); filter: blur(2px); }
      100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); filter: blur(0); }
    }
  `;
  document.head.appendChild(dynamicStyle);
</script>
</body>
</html>
